Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:39.15,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:47.62,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:55.79,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:23:03.97,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:10.91,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:21.32,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:30.93,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
